1
00:01:28,780 --> 00:01:35,000
[Strange Tales of Tang Dynasty III:
To Chang'an]

2
00:01:35,650 --> 00:01:37,900
[Episode 2]

3
00:01:43,870 --> 00:01:44,729
Grand General.

4
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:45,800
You're awake.

5
00:01:47,950 --> 00:01:48,950
Don't scratch it!

6
00:01:49,120 --> 00:01:50,229
You have to tend it well.

7
00:01:50,229 --> 00:01:52,390
The wound will mend within ten days.

8
00:01:52,950 --> 00:01:53,759
You must be

9
00:01:54,590 --> 00:01:57,370
the Miracle Doctor Fei who saved my life?

10
00:01:58,039 --> 00:01:59,509
That's me.

11
00:02:00,590 --> 00:02:02,480
Jsut call me Master Ji.

12
00:02:03,680 --> 00:02:05,790
Or Benefactor, if you prefer.

13
00:02:06,590 --> 00:02:08,199
Go get Lu Lingfeng.

14
00:02:16,840 --> 00:02:17,360
Fei.

15
00:02:18,400 --> 00:02:19,250
Here's the wine I got for you.

16
00:02:19,250 --> 00:02:20,840
[Crimson Blood and Loyal Heart]

17
00:02:21,430 --> 00:02:22,590
You're back just in time.

18
00:02:22,590 --> 00:02:24,120
He's asking for you inside.

19
00:02:24,360 --> 00:02:25,890
The Grand General is awake!

20
00:02:26,600 --> 00:02:29,180
[Crimson Blood and Loyal Heart]

21
00:02:29,680 --> 00:02:30,540
Grand General.

22
00:02:30,960 --> 00:02:31,760
Rest assured,

23
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:33,329
no matter when

24
00:02:33,750 --> 00:02:35,280
or what injustice I suffer,

25
00:02:35,310 --> 00:02:36,170
I, Lu Lingfeng,

26
00:02:36,280 --> 00:02:38,030
will never harbor any personal grudge

27
00:02:38,030 --> 00:02:39,230
against His Majesty.

28
00:02:40,190 --> 00:02:41,120
Because my heart

29
00:02:41,590 --> 00:02:43,450
remains loyal to the Tang Empire.

30
00:02:44,630 --> 00:02:45,280
Good.

31
00:02:45,470 --> 00:02:47,280
That's exactly what I wanted to hear.

32
00:02:47,280 --> 00:02:48,770
Prepare the horses.
Follow me to the palace.

33
00:02:48,770 --> 00:02:50,120
You can't ride a horse yet.

34
00:02:50,120 --> 00:02:51,750
I must see His Majesty immediately

35
00:02:51,750 --> 00:02:53,780
to recommend you as my successor.

36
00:02:54,870 --> 00:02:55,730
Grand General!

37
00:02:57,000 --> 00:02:58,260
I must see the Emperor.

38
00:02:58,310 --> 00:02:59,470
From today on,

39
00:02:59,960 --> 00:03:03,220
you will be the Grand General
of the Right Imperial Guards.

40
00:04:04,750 --> 00:04:05,280
Fei!

41
00:04:07,110 --> 00:04:07,790
Master Ji!

42
00:04:24,220 --> 00:04:25,420
-General.
-General.

43
00:04:25,510 --> 00:04:26,000
Fei!

44
00:04:26,630 --> 00:04:27,800
Don't move me!

45
00:04:54,920 --> 00:04:56,120
My ribs

46
00:04:56,750 --> 00:04:57,830
and my leg bones

47
00:04:58,630 --> 00:05:00,560
are broken in at least four places.

48
00:05:01,830 --> 00:05:02,480
Be gentle.

49
00:05:03,390 --> 00:05:04,190
In this world,

50
00:05:04,750 --> 00:05:08,000
the only person who can set his own bones

51
00:05:08,410 --> 00:05:11,000
is none other than me, Fei Yingjun.

52
00:05:11,720 --> 00:05:13,390
Fei, stop bragging.

53
00:05:13,690 --> 00:05:15,550
Look how exhausted Miss Xijun is.

54
00:05:15,720 --> 00:05:18,190
Xijun is clever
and has medicine knowledge.

55
00:05:18,390 --> 00:05:19,520
She learns quickly.

56
00:05:20,190 --> 00:05:20,850
Otherwise,

57
00:05:21,480 --> 00:05:23,280
I, Master Ji, would be finished.

58
00:05:24,270 --> 00:05:25,270
You saved my life.

59
00:05:25,830 --> 00:05:27,160
I should repay you.

60
00:05:29,690 --> 00:05:30,310
Xijun,

61
00:05:31,270 --> 00:05:32,630
open my right hand.

62
00:05:41,560 --> 00:05:43,020
A feather from the raptor?

63
00:05:44,750 --> 00:05:45,350
Master Ji,

64
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:46,690
in that moment of danger,

65
00:05:46,690 --> 00:05:48,890
you still thought to pluck its feather?

66
00:05:49,270 --> 00:05:51,950
That's called staying calm in a crisis.

67
00:05:52,830 --> 00:05:54,430
Or not leaving empty-handed,
if you prefer.

68
00:05:54,430 --> 00:05:55,830
Even if I fell to my death,

69
00:05:55,920 --> 00:05:57,780
I had to grab at least one feather.

70
00:05:58,830 --> 00:06:00,030
Give it to Lu Lingfeng

71
00:06:00,310 --> 00:06:01,950
so he can identify what bird it was.

72
00:06:01,950 --> 00:06:03,350
He will surely thank you.

73
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:04,160
Doctor Fei.

74
00:06:05,720 --> 00:06:06,450
Lu Lingfeng.

75
00:06:06,560 --> 00:06:07,870
A feather Master Ji plucked

76
00:06:07,870 --> 00:06:09,070
from the raptor's body.

77
00:06:09,070 --> 00:06:09,930
Keep it for now.

78
00:06:14,040 --> 00:06:15,240
How are his injuries?

79
00:06:15,390 --> 00:06:16,120
Don't worry.

80
00:06:16,350 --> 00:06:17,630
He won't die.

81
00:06:18,190 --> 00:06:19,560
You saved me this time.

82
00:06:20,560 --> 00:06:21,070
Thank you.

83
00:06:21,070 --> 00:06:22,130
No need to thank me.

84
00:06:22,750 --> 00:06:23,870
Since you're not going to die,

85
00:06:23,870 --> 00:06:24,670
let me ask you.

86
00:06:25,390 --> 00:06:26,480
What is this?

87
00:06:30,480 --> 00:06:31,360
Last night,

88
00:06:31,810 --> 00:06:33,580
I saw three golden peaches

89
00:06:33,800 --> 00:06:35,060
rolling on the ground.

90
00:06:35,190 --> 00:06:35,990
I thought

91
00:06:36,310 --> 00:06:38,000
since you were with His Majesty,

92
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:39,430
you must have eaten some already.

93
00:06:39,430 --> 00:06:41,510
I got these three myself,

94
00:06:41,950 --> 00:06:43,510
and I'm the oldest,

95
00:06:43,720 --> 00:06:46,250
so it's not too much to have one myself,
right?

96
00:06:48,720 --> 00:06:50,159
The Kang Kingdom's golden peach,

97
00:06:50,159 --> 00:06:51,480
truly worthy of being a tribute.

98
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:52,240
Wonderful!

99
00:06:52,510 --> 00:06:53,190
Wonderful!

100
00:06:54,190 --> 00:06:55,510
The remaining two

101
00:06:56,159 --> 00:06:58,290
can be shared among the four of them.

102
00:06:58,560 --> 00:07:00,010
Isn't that fair?

103
00:07:00,120 --> 00:07:01,850
But you didn't leave any for us!

104
00:07:03,870 --> 00:07:05,160
Blame it on

105
00:07:06,270 --> 00:07:08,110
the golden peach's divine taste.

106
00:07:08,110 --> 00:07:08,600
It...

107
00:07:08,870 --> 00:07:11,330
It was luring me at every turn.

108
00:07:11,600 --> 00:07:13,130
These three golden peaches

109
00:07:13,680 --> 00:07:15,430
were actually rewards
that I requested from His Majesty

110
00:07:15,430 --> 00:07:16,840
for all of you.

111
00:07:17,430 --> 00:07:18,870
You ate them all by yourself

112
00:07:18,870 --> 00:07:20,240
and then blame the peaches?

113
00:07:20,240 --> 00:07:20,600
You...

114
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:21,070
Enough.

115
00:07:21,830 --> 00:07:23,360
Though Master Ji is greedy,

116
00:07:23,510 --> 00:07:25,170
he has already been punished.

117
00:07:25,620 --> 00:07:27,020
Don't blame him anymore.

118
00:07:36,690 --> 00:07:38,290
They've all had the peaches.

119
00:07:39,430 --> 00:07:40,230
What's wrong?

120
00:07:46,230 --> 00:07:48,159
Thank you for reminding me, Xijun.

121
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:56,250
You want to use my palace token?

122
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:58,159
I must go to the palace immediately

123
00:07:58,159 --> 00:07:59,220
to see His Majesty.

124
00:08:00,870 --> 00:08:01,430
Yes.

125
00:08:02,410 --> 00:08:03,540
The Imperial Guards

126
00:08:04,070 --> 00:08:06,270
cannot go a day without the Grand General.

127
00:08:06,270 --> 00:08:07,130
Bring me paper.

128
00:08:07,720 --> 00:08:09,980
I'll write a blood letter
recommending you.

129
00:08:09,980 --> 00:08:10,840
Grand General,

130
00:08:10,920 --> 00:08:12,250
that's not why I'm here.

131
00:08:12,800 --> 00:08:13,720
Then why?

132
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:18,330
The golden peaches from the Kang Kingdom.

133
00:08:19,620 --> 00:08:20,240
What?

134
00:08:21,720 --> 00:08:23,780
That evil bird has entered Chang'an?

135
00:08:31,970 --> 00:08:33,630
Is the Grand General alright?

136
00:08:33,630 --> 00:08:34,240
This time, the raptor

137
00:08:34,240 --> 00:08:35,669
did not attack the Grand General.

138
00:08:35,669 --> 00:08:36,409
Instead, it targeted

139
00:08:36,409 --> 00:08:38,030
Fei Yingjun, who was treating
the Grand General's wounds.

140
00:08:38,030 --> 00:08:40,549
Whether it's Your Majesty,
the Grand General, or Fei,

141
00:08:40,549 --> 00:08:41,630
before being attacked,

142
00:08:41,630 --> 00:08:43,429
they all had one thing in common.

143
00:08:43,440 --> 00:08:45,500
They had just eaten the golden peach.

144
00:08:49,480 --> 00:08:50,390
You mean...

145
00:08:51,670 --> 00:08:52,320
That bird

146
00:08:53,270 --> 00:08:55,920
only attacks people
who have just eaten the golden peaches?

147
00:08:55,920 --> 00:08:57,240
Although it's just a guess,

148
00:08:57,240 --> 00:08:58,640
I humbly beg Your Majesty

149
00:08:58,670 --> 00:09:00,330
not to eat any golden peaches.

150
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:06,600
Could it be

151
00:09:07,390 --> 00:09:09,320
that Your Majesty has just eaten some?

152
00:09:09,320 --> 00:09:10,120
No, I haven't.

153
00:09:11,560 --> 00:09:12,890
However, as per custom,

154
00:09:13,100 --> 00:09:14,510
tributes from foreign kingdoms

155
00:09:14,510 --> 00:09:15,730
have already been distributed
to the Retired Emperor,

156
00:09:15,730 --> 00:09:16,990
the Grand Princess...

157
00:09:17,020 --> 00:09:18,790
As well as various nobles and relatives,

158
00:09:18,790 --> 00:09:20,460
and meritorious ministers.

159
00:09:21,710 --> 00:09:24,440
I respectfully urge Your Majesty
to act swiftly.

160
00:09:24,770 --> 00:09:27,230
Recall all the golden peaches immediately.

161
00:09:27,240 --> 00:09:29,020
I will personally meet the Retired Emperor

162
00:09:29,020 --> 00:09:30,820
to explain the situation to him.

163
00:09:38,790 --> 00:09:39,650
Your Highness.

164
00:09:58,200 --> 00:09:58,530
Do you know

165
00:09:58,530 --> 00:09:59,600
[Retired Emperor]

166
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:01,080
when I first tasted

167
00:10:01,120 --> 00:10:02,380
these golden peaches,

168
00:10:02,440 --> 00:10:03,240
how old was I?

169
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:07,660
I was two years old.

170
00:10:09,480 --> 00:10:11,360
That year, Liu Rengui

171
00:10:12,390 --> 00:10:13,920
annihilated the Wa Kingdom

172
00:10:14,400 --> 00:10:15,280
at Baijiangkou

173
00:10:15,550 --> 00:10:16,750
in Baekji.

174
00:10:17,150 --> 00:10:17,960
Emperor Gaozong

175
00:10:17,960 --> 00:10:20,220
held a grand fruit banquet to celebrate.

176
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:21,510
It just so happened

177
00:10:21,510 --> 00:10:24,640
that the Tang envoys
returning from the Western Regions

178
00:10:24,910 --> 00:10:28,040
brought back a few golden peaches
from the Kang Kingdom.

179
00:10:28,390 --> 00:10:30,280
Father placed one peach

180
00:10:30,410 --> 00:10:31,430
in my hands.

181
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:33,270
But at that time,

182
00:10:33,670 --> 00:10:36,410
I didn't have all my teeth yet.

183
00:10:36,630 --> 00:10:37,690
How could I bite it?

184
00:10:38,440 --> 00:10:39,170
Father said,

185
00:10:39,630 --> 00:10:40,560
"The people of Wa

186
00:10:41,030 --> 00:10:41,890
fear strength,

187
00:10:42,790 --> 00:10:43,670
not virtue.

188
00:10:44,360 --> 00:10:45,240
This war

189
00:10:45,910 --> 00:10:48,270
showed the might of the Tang Empire.

190
00:10:48,670 --> 00:10:50,130
Even if you cannot bite it,

191
00:10:50,560 --> 00:10:52,420
you must suck its juice fiercely.

192
00:10:52,910 --> 00:10:54,080
As a royal child,

193
00:10:54,530 --> 00:10:57,960
you should celebrate with the empire."

194
00:10:59,680 --> 00:11:00,750
So I did as told.

195
00:11:01,780 --> 00:11:03,790
Guess what happened?

196
00:11:09,260 --> 00:11:10,480
Emperor Gaozong

197
00:11:12,750 --> 00:11:14,270
said I showed promise,

198
00:11:17,390 --> 00:11:18,320
and that someday

199
00:11:19,480 --> 00:11:21,390
he would pass the throne to me.

200
00:11:23,600 --> 00:11:24,840
Decades have passed.

201
00:11:28,790 --> 00:11:30,920
Emperor Gaozong's imperial presence

202
00:11:33,200 --> 00:11:34,030
seems

203
00:11:36,630 --> 00:11:38,750
to still linger before my eyes.

204
00:11:55,790 --> 00:11:57,720
Your Majesty, please don't eat it.

205
00:12:00,080 --> 00:12:00,750
Father,

206
00:12:01,320 --> 00:12:03,180
you mustn't eat the golden peach.

207
00:12:10,080 --> 00:12:11,840
The golden peaches from the Kang Kingdom

208
00:12:11,840 --> 00:12:13,570
are for Your Highness to enjoy.

209
00:12:14,270 --> 00:12:15,120
Your Highness,

210
00:12:15,120 --> 00:12:16,230
Lu Lingfeng is here.

211
00:12:16,230 --> 00:12:17,600
My son has come to see me!

212
00:12:17,870 --> 00:12:18,320
Quick,

213
00:12:18,640 --> 00:12:19,270
bring him in.

214
00:12:19,270 --> 00:12:20,130
Your Highness,

215
00:12:20,390 --> 00:12:22,050
please don't eat the peaches.

216
00:12:26,320 --> 00:12:28,360
Lu Lingfeng pays respects
to Your Highness.

217
00:12:28,360 --> 00:12:29,820
May Your Highness be well.

218
00:12:42,280 --> 00:12:43,800
My son, please rise.

219
00:12:48,550 --> 00:12:49,810
I heard from Su Wuming

220
00:12:49,910 --> 00:12:52,910
that your journey to the West
was fraught with danger.

221
00:12:52,960 --> 00:12:54,630
You must have suffered greatly.

222
00:12:54,630 --> 00:12:55,200
Come,

223
00:12:55,910 --> 00:12:57,120
tell me all about it.

224
00:12:58,080 --> 00:12:58,870
Your Highness.

225
00:12:58,870 --> 00:13:00,030
I've come here on a matter

226
00:13:00,030 --> 00:13:01,430
of a greater importance.

227
00:13:01,620 --> 00:13:03,220
I must implore Your Highness

228
00:13:03,440 --> 00:13:05,240
not to eat these golden peaches.

229
00:13:11,370 --> 00:13:12,030
Why not?

230
00:13:15,200 --> 00:13:15,960
My dear son,

231
00:13:16,360 --> 00:13:17,420
you worry too much.

232
00:13:17,630 --> 00:13:19,480
Come, join me

233
00:13:19,600 --> 00:13:22,480
in enjoying the finest fruit in the world.

234
00:13:23,910 --> 00:13:24,670
Your Highness,

235
00:13:24,670 --> 00:13:27,200
you really must not
eat these golden peaches.

236
00:13:32,080 --> 00:13:33,120
My son

237
00:13:34,000 --> 00:13:35,460
being concerned about me.

238
00:13:35,790 --> 00:13:37,240
I feel glad.

239
00:13:37,720 --> 00:13:39,550
But, I don't believe

240
00:13:40,200 --> 00:13:41,550
what you've just said.

241
00:13:41,870 --> 00:13:44,240
Although you're also Master Di's disciple,

242
00:13:44,240 --> 00:13:46,390
when it comes to investigation skills,

243
00:13:46,390 --> 00:13:48,390
you're still no match for Su Wuming.

244
00:13:49,000 --> 00:13:50,390
Do you know why?

245
00:13:54,270 --> 00:13:55,800
Because you're too honest,

246
00:13:56,100 --> 00:13:56,840
naive,

247
00:13:57,390 --> 00:13:58,510
and easily fooled.

248
00:13:59,750 --> 00:14:01,370
Eating this golden peach

249
00:14:01,550 --> 00:14:03,260
will attract raptors.

250
00:14:05,030 --> 00:14:06,330
How is that possible?

251
00:14:06,750 --> 00:14:08,110
This must be someone

252
00:14:08,150 --> 00:14:09,970
close to His Majesty

253
00:14:10,200 --> 00:14:12,510
who made this up just to trick you.

254
00:14:12,910 --> 00:14:13,770
Your Highness,

255
00:14:13,790 --> 00:14:14,850
it's not like that.

256
00:14:16,270 --> 00:14:16,910
Guards!

257
00:14:17,270 --> 00:14:17,870
Yes!

258
00:14:18,270 --> 00:14:20,930
Set up a golden peach banquet
in the back garden.

259
00:14:28,360 --> 00:14:29,420
Has the golden peaches sent to my aunt

260
00:14:29,420 --> 00:14:30,350
been retrieved?

261
00:14:31,480 --> 00:14:32,080
No.

262
00:14:33,510 --> 00:14:34,200
You fool!

263
00:14:34,460 --> 00:14:35,630
Your Majesty, please calm down.

264
00:14:35,630 --> 00:14:36,940
It's not that I didn't try,

265
00:14:36,940 --> 00:14:38,140
but there was no need.

266
00:14:38,500 --> 00:14:40,080
Lu Lingfeng has already rushed

267
00:14:40,080 --> 00:14:41,780
to the Princess's Mansion to inform them.

268
00:14:41,780 --> 00:14:43,050
If I sent more people,

269
00:14:43,150 --> 00:14:44,750
wouldn't that be redundant?

270
00:14:49,080 --> 00:14:49,630
Cen Zhi.

271
00:14:50,080 --> 00:14:51,240
Tell the guards to be on high alert,

272
00:14:51,240 --> 00:14:51,510
[Radiance in Harmony]

273
00:14:51,510 --> 00:14:52,510
prepare plenty of bows and arrows,

274
00:14:52,510 --> 00:14:53,870
and watch for raptors in the sky.

275
00:14:53,870 --> 00:14:54,550
Do not fail.

276
00:14:55,120 --> 00:14:55,630
You're

277
00:14:56,270 --> 00:14:57,120
ordering me?

278
00:14:58,760 --> 00:14:59,870
Just do as he says.

279
00:15:01,630 --> 00:15:02,270
Yes.

280
00:15:17,130 --> 00:15:17,990
Your Highness.

281
00:15:21,950 --> 00:15:23,480
It's delicious.

282
00:15:31,180 --> 00:15:33,630
You're so worried about birds

283
00:15:33,630 --> 00:15:34,870
coming to harm me.

284
00:15:35,510 --> 00:15:37,550
Such filial devotion.

285
00:15:38,150 --> 00:15:39,390
During this western journey,

286
00:15:39,390 --> 00:15:40,860
we've been separated.

287
00:15:40,900 --> 00:15:43,270
Have you missed me, your mother?

288
00:15:43,600 --> 00:15:46,840
I've been thinking of you day and night
in Chang'an,

289
00:15:46,870 --> 00:15:48,400
heartbroken with longing.

290
00:15:48,870 --> 00:15:50,840
Yesterday, Su Wuming said

291
00:15:51,440 --> 00:15:53,520
that my life has been glorious

292
00:15:53,550 --> 00:15:55,080
and should have no regrets.

293
00:15:55,320 --> 00:15:56,720
Little does he know

294
00:15:58,440 --> 00:16:00,720
that my greatest regret in life

295
00:16:03,360 --> 00:16:05,290
is not being able to accompany you.

296
00:16:12,720 --> 00:16:13,020
[Radiance in Harmony]

297
00:16:13,020 --> 00:16:13,880
Give me the bow.

298
00:16:15,150 --> 00:16:15,670
You!

299
00:16:15,870 --> 00:16:17,720
Look how nervous my son is.

300
00:16:19,390 --> 00:16:19,970
Cen Zhi,

301
00:16:21,080 --> 00:16:23,440
since he's willing to protect me,

302
00:16:24,080 --> 00:16:26,340
you should sit down and eat some peaches.

303
00:16:26,600 --> 00:16:27,460
If that's so...

304
00:16:27,600 --> 00:16:28,840
Thank you, Your Highness.

305
00:16:28,840 --> 00:16:29,670
Sit here.

306
00:16:31,600 --> 00:16:32,530
I wouldn't dare.

307
00:16:32,600 --> 00:16:33,370
Take a seat.

308
00:16:34,720 --> 00:16:35,200
Yes.

309
00:16:35,350 --> 00:16:36,390
[Radiance in Harmony]

310
00:16:36,390 --> 00:16:38,000
You lost an arm

311
00:16:38,020 --> 00:16:39,490
protecting me.

312
00:16:39,960 --> 00:16:41,620
Your loyalty is commendable.

313
00:16:41,930 --> 00:16:44,060
In the future, you and Chancellor Cui,

314
00:16:44,510 --> 00:16:46,040
one civil and one military,

315
00:16:46,630 --> 00:16:50,390
will be my most trusted officials.

316
00:16:50,700 --> 00:16:51,080
[Radiance in Harmony]

317
00:16:51,080 --> 00:16:52,880
Thank you again, Your Highness.

318
00:16:53,630 --> 00:16:54,270
Eat up.

319
00:16:54,670 --> 00:16:55,360
Yes.

320
00:17:01,320 --> 00:17:01,930
Ji.

321
00:17:04,640 --> 00:17:05,510
Come up here.

322
00:17:09,960 --> 00:17:11,829
You really refuse to eat the peaches?

323
00:17:11,829 --> 00:17:13,310
That strange bird is fierce.

324
00:17:13,310 --> 00:17:14,369
I beg Your Highness

325
00:17:15,670 --> 00:17:16,730
to eat less of them.

326
00:17:21,490 --> 00:17:22,359
Soldiers,

327
00:17:23,030 --> 00:17:24,550
you have been guarding my safety

328
00:17:24,550 --> 00:17:25,940
day and night.

329
00:17:26,310 --> 00:17:27,910
Thank you for your hard work.

330
00:17:27,920 --> 00:17:28,750
Today,

331
00:17:29,000 --> 00:17:31,400
the golden peaches
offered by the Kang Kingdom

332
00:17:31,400 --> 00:17:32,860
have arrived in Chang'an.

333
00:17:33,270 --> 00:17:35,880
They taste exquisite.

334
00:17:36,130 --> 00:17:38,270
I'm rewarding each of you
with half a peach

335
00:17:38,270 --> 00:17:39,480
and a cup of fine wine.

336
00:17:40,200 --> 00:17:44,390
You may drink with me at the same table.

337
00:17:46,000 --> 00:17:47,710
Thank you, Your Highness.

338
00:17:50,650 --> 00:17:52,160
[Observations from a Journey West]

339
00:17:57,350 --> 00:17:59,070
From the Princess's Mansion...

340
00:17:59,070 --> 00:18:00,530
There's still no news yet.

341
00:18:00,790 --> 00:18:01,350
I think

342
00:18:01,510 --> 00:18:03,200
Lu Lingfeng must have warned her in time,

343
00:18:03,200 --> 00:18:06,060
so Her Highness didn't dare eat
the golden peaches.

344
00:18:06,590 --> 00:18:07,790
In critical moments,

345
00:18:07,830 --> 00:18:09,880
Lu Lingfeng only thought
about Her Highness.

346
00:18:09,880 --> 00:18:12,280
He cannot be trusted with important tasks.

347
00:18:13,400 --> 00:18:15,200
I'm more worried about Aunt now.

348
00:18:16,510 --> 00:18:17,970
She loves eating peaches,

349
00:18:18,420 --> 00:18:21,310
especially the golden peaches
from the Kang Kingdom.

350
00:18:21,310 --> 00:18:22,570
With her temperament,

351
00:18:23,200 --> 00:18:26,510
I fear Lu Lingfeng won't be able
to dissuade her.

352
00:18:30,640 --> 00:18:33,240
Thank you for your generosity,
Your Highness.

353
00:18:37,640 --> 00:18:39,240
Once the golden peach enters my mouth,

354
00:18:39,240 --> 00:18:40,640
its flavor lingers on the lips and teeth.

355
00:18:40,640 --> 00:18:41,960
How fortunate am I

356
00:18:42,160 --> 00:18:43,200
to be able to taste

357
00:18:43,350 --> 00:18:45,350
the most precious fruit in the world.

358
00:18:45,350 --> 00:18:46,000
I will

359
00:18:46,550 --> 00:18:48,640
remember this taste for a lifetime.

360
00:18:48,770 --> 00:18:49,240
[Radiance in Harmony]

361
00:18:49,240 --> 00:18:50,720
Thank you again, Your Highness.

362
00:18:50,720 --> 00:18:52,120
I shall take my leave now.

363
00:18:53,880 --> 00:18:54,440
Cen Zhi,

364
00:18:55,200 --> 00:18:56,250
you may go too.

365
00:18:56,960 --> 00:18:57,550
Yes.

366
00:19:04,480 --> 00:19:05,200
Ji.

367
00:19:09,270 --> 00:19:09,880
Come.

368
00:19:12,290 --> 00:19:14,790
[Radiance in Harmony]

369
00:19:18,350 --> 00:19:19,350
Don't worry.

370
00:19:20,240 --> 00:19:21,660
Whatever raptor

371
00:19:22,000 --> 00:19:23,000
or evil bird it is,

372
00:19:23,750 --> 00:19:25,960
it won't come to my residence.

373
00:19:27,160 --> 00:19:29,040
That person ate the peach

374
00:19:29,240 --> 00:19:31,520
and was attacked by the raptor.

375
00:19:31,720 --> 00:19:33,380
It's because he wasn't worthy

376
00:19:34,240 --> 00:19:37,030
of enjoying this great empire.

377
00:19:37,280 --> 00:19:38,200
Now,

378
00:19:38,510 --> 00:19:41,940
only I can lead the Tang Empire

379
00:19:42,420 --> 00:19:43,790
to glory.

380
00:19:50,890 --> 00:19:51,690
What's wrong?

381
00:19:53,680 --> 00:19:56,110
You don't agree with what I said?

382
00:19:58,950 --> 00:20:00,020
My father,

383
00:20:01,070 --> 00:20:01,960
mother,

384
00:20:02,770 --> 00:20:04,200
and two brothers

385
00:20:04,810 --> 00:20:05,870
were all emperors.

386
00:20:06,270 --> 00:20:09,010
Now even my nephew

387
00:20:09,510 --> 00:20:10,920
has become emperor.

388
00:20:12,120 --> 00:20:13,820
As the one and only

389
00:20:13,880 --> 00:20:16,440
Grand Princess of the Tang Empire,

390
00:20:17,590 --> 00:20:19,030
why shouldn't I?

391
00:20:21,900 --> 00:20:23,570
Look into my eyes.

392
00:20:27,410 --> 00:20:28,510
I have four sons,

393
00:20:30,310 --> 00:20:31,110
but only you

394
00:20:32,270 --> 00:20:34,360
excel in both civil and military affairs,

395
00:20:34,360 --> 00:20:35,780
have endured hardships,

396
00:20:36,030 --> 00:20:37,270
remain resilient,

397
00:20:37,880 --> 00:20:39,810
are selfless at heart,

398
00:20:40,200 --> 00:20:41,930
and have the world in your mind.

399
00:20:43,640 --> 00:20:45,410
Bear my surname, Li.

400
00:20:46,080 --> 00:20:46,970
In the future,

401
00:20:47,830 --> 00:20:49,870
I will pass the Tang Empire

402
00:20:50,350 --> 00:20:51,240
to you.

403
00:21:04,720 --> 00:21:05,450
Cen Dianjun.

404
00:21:06,000 --> 00:21:08,240
Did anyone leave the Princess's Mansion
tonight?

405
00:21:08,240 --> 00:21:08,700
No.

406
00:21:08,880 --> 00:21:10,340
Good. Prepare the horses.

407
00:21:10,440 --> 00:21:10,960
Yes.

408
00:21:13,260 --> 00:21:16,140
[Sangma Eatery]

409
00:22:22,060 --> 00:22:23,310
Cen Zhi is dead?

410
00:22:23,310 --> 00:22:23,590
[Ruling with the Harmony of the Qin]

411
00:22:23,590 --> 00:22:24,680
He was lifted into the air,

412
00:22:24,680 --> 00:22:25,700
dropped three times,

413
00:22:25,700 --> 00:22:27,590
and then disemboweled
by that vicious bird.

414
00:22:27,590 --> 00:22:28,520
It was horrific.

415
00:22:32,240 --> 00:22:33,170
Any news on Aunt?

416
00:22:33,960 --> 00:22:34,640
I heard Her Highness

417
00:22:34,640 --> 00:22:36,830
held a golden peach banquet
in the back garden.

418
00:22:36,830 --> 00:22:37,400
Even the guards

419
00:22:37,400 --> 00:22:38,880
were rewarded with tribute peaches
and wine.

420
00:22:38,880 --> 00:22:40,140
But except for Cen Zhi,

421
00:22:40,150 --> 00:22:41,240
no one was attacked.

422
00:22:41,240 --> 00:22:42,440
Where did Cen Zhi die?

423
00:22:42,880 --> 00:22:43,880
Not far from here.

424
00:22:44,590 --> 00:22:45,810
He must have been coming

425
00:22:45,810 --> 00:22:47,410
to report information to me.

426
00:22:47,940 --> 00:22:49,680
The situation has been extremely tense
lately.

427
00:22:49,680 --> 00:22:52,210
I ordered him to report any news
immediately.

428
00:22:58,650 --> 00:22:59,640
Kill me then.

429
00:23:00,470 --> 00:23:02,800
I will be remembered throughout history.

430
00:23:03,400 --> 00:23:04,850
People will call me

431
00:23:05,270 --> 00:23:07,600
the most loyal servant of the Tang Empire.

432
00:23:07,830 --> 00:23:08,510
As for you,

433
00:23:09,550 --> 00:23:11,260
all sixteen members of your family

434
00:23:11,260 --> 00:23:12,500
are in my custody.

435
00:23:14,110 --> 00:23:15,320
Your little son

436
00:23:15,760 --> 00:23:16,890
is four months old.

437
00:23:19,440 --> 00:23:20,590
His little face

438
00:23:21,480 --> 00:23:22,990
is so soft and rosy.

439
00:23:24,590 --> 00:23:26,070
Absolutely adorable.

440
00:23:39,240 --> 00:23:40,370
I already suspected

441
00:23:40,390 --> 00:23:42,240
that this vicious bird
was connected to Her Highness.

442
00:23:42,240 --> 00:23:43,370
Now it's confirmed.

443
00:23:43,960 --> 00:23:45,720
Everyone who ate the golden peaches,

444
00:23:45,720 --> 00:23:47,350
as long as stayed
within the Princess's Mansion,

445
00:23:47,350 --> 00:23:48,880
remained completely safe.

446
00:23:49,440 --> 00:23:50,830
Cen Zhi was the only one.

447
00:23:52,790 --> 00:23:53,560
This proves

448
00:23:54,560 --> 00:23:55,480
that this vicious bird

449
00:23:55,480 --> 00:23:57,410
is kept by the Princess's Mansion.

450
00:23:58,070 --> 00:23:58,750
Therefore,

451
00:23:59,630 --> 00:24:01,890
it doesn't attack people in its own home.

452
00:24:03,310 --> 00:24:04,180
Nonsense.

453
00:24:04,790 --> 00:24:05,680
[Ruling with the Harmony of the Qin]

454
00:24:05,680 --> 00:24:06,940
Who do you think she is?

455
00:24:07,400 --> 00:24:09,800
Would she need to keep birds
to harm people?

456
00:24:10,160 --> 00:24:11,020
You servant,

457
00:24:11,400 --> 00:24:13,800
stop making wild speculations out of fear.

458
00:24:15,590 --> 00:24:17,570
Cen Zhi. Oh, Cen Zhi.

459
00:24:18,070 --> 00:24:18,730
In the past,

460
00:24:19,100 --> 00:24:20,750
Your Highness transferred him

461
00:24:20,750 --> 00:24:22,370
from the northern city to the capital

462
00:24:22,370 --> 00:24:24,370
was because you valued his loyalty.

463
00:24:24,790 --> 00:24:27,960
Who would have thought
after the Chengfo Temple incident,

464
00:24:27,960 --> 00:24:29,500
he would betray us.

465
00:24:30,160 --> 00:24:32,290
He truly deserved his fate.

466
00:24:32,680 --> 00:24:33,960
I don't blame him.

467
00:24:34,880 --> 00:24:37,160
If anyone is to blame,

468
00:24:37,890 --> 00:24:39,880
it's that person being overtly ruthless.

469
00:24:39,880 --> 00:24:42,310
He even hold Cen Zhi's family hostage.

470
00:24:43,780 --> 00:24:44,710
Chancellor Cui,

471
00:24:47,440 --> 00:24:49,780
what would you do
if you were in his place?

472
00:24:52,120 --> 00:24:54,200
I would never betray Your Highness.

473
00:24:54,510 --> 00:24:57,600
If the person you love most

474
00:24:58,000 --> 00:24:59,590
fell into enemy hands,

475
00:25:00,750 --> 00:25:01,680
Chancellor Cui,

476
00:25:02,500 --> 00:25:04,180
what then?

477
00:25:06,070 --> 00:25:08,530
I swear to follow Your Highness
until death.

478
00:25:08,590 --> 00:25:09,310
I have already

479
00:25:09,310 --> 00:25:11,540
cast aside all personal attachments.

480
00:25:11,680 --> 00:25:13,550
I only wish for Your Highness
to achieve greatness.

481
00:25:13,550 --> 00:25:14,890
I long to see

482
00:25:14,960 --> 00:25:16,580
a stronger Tang Empire

483
00:25:16,720 --> 00:25:19,070
under the rule of a new empress.

484
00:25:22,730 --> 00:25:24,330
If that day truly comes,

485
00:25:25,270 --> 00:25:26,960
I will not disappoint you.

486
00:25:46,030 --> 00:25:47,060
It's full now.

487
00:25:53,080 --> 00:25:54,890
It was hungry for too long.

488
00:25:55,750 --> 00:25:57,990
It's extremely happy today.

489
00:25:59,030 --> 00:26:00,190
But I want to know

490
00:26:00,530 --> 00:26:02,920
why it didn't go
to the golden peach banquet

491
00:26:02,920 --> 00:26:04,450
at the Princess's Mansion.

492
00:26:05,630 --> 00:26:07,830
There are places birds don't want to go.

493
00:26:08,030 --> 00:26:09,490
The wings are on its body,

494
00:26:10,480 --> 00:26:11,680
what can I do about it?

495
00:26:12,370 --> 00:26:14,200
You're hiding something from me.

496
00:26:14,200 --> 00:26:14,860
No, I'm not.

497
00:26:15,620 --> 00:26:17,500
If the Princess's Mansion
can hold a golden peach banquet,

498
00:26:17,500 --> 00:26:19,990
it means they don't suspect
the golden peaches.

499
00:26:19,990 --> 00:26:21,450
So there's still a chance.

500
00:26:21,850 --> 00:26:24,850
My bird will be working hard lately.

501
00:26:26,030 --> 00:26:26,900
What if there are places

502
00:26:26,900 --> 00:26:28,500
where birds don't want to go?

503
00:26:30,540 --> 00:26:32,110
Our great undertaking is not yet complete.

504
00:26:32,110 --> 00:26:34,310
We must be united in purpose and effort.

505
00:26:35,550 --> 00:26:37,950
Are you really not hiding anything
from me?

506
00:26:38,170 --> 00:26:38,750
No!

507
00:26:39,960 --> 00:26:41,050
When the time is right,

508
00:26:41,050 --> 00:26:42,440
places where birds don't want to go,

509
00:26:42,440 --> 00:26:43,680
I'll go instead.

510
00:27:02,190 --> 00:27:04,200
[Prison of Gantang County]

511
00:27:26,830 --> 00:27:28,690
You don't want to starve anymore?

512
00:27:31,020 --> 00:27:34,180
But today's food
has already been distributed.

513
00:27:35,040 --> 00:27:35,530
This portion

514
00:27:35,530 --> 00:27:36,680
[Liu XVIII] [Liu XIX]

515
00:27:36,680 --> 00:27:37,930
is mine.

516
00:28:00,680 --> 00:28:01,750
You insolent savage!

517
00:28:01,750 --> 00:28:03,210
How dare you attack Mr. Su!

518
00:28:05,420 --> 00:28:06,820
Yingtao, don't hurt him.

519
00:28:33,300 --> 00:28:34,030
Sheriff Xu.

520
00:28:35,500 --> 00:28:36,960
You've been starving him.

521
00:28:37,920 --> 00:28:38,480
No,

522
00:28:38,750 --> 00:28:40,680
he himself went on a hunger strike.

523
00:28:41,070 --> 00:28:41,930
Hunger strike?

524
00:28:43,030 --> 00:28:44,090
Since last autumn,

525
00:28:44,160 --> 00:28:45,290
when Liu XVII was executed,

526
00:28:45,290 --> 00:28:46,350
he went mad with rage.

527
00:28:46,350 --> 00:28:47,830
He had bitten several guards,

528
00:28:47,830 --> 00:28:49,270
so we had to put him in a cage.

529
00:28:49,270 --> 00:28:51,000
Only then did he calm down a bit.

530
00:28:51,480 --> 00:28:53,680
Liu XVIII, however,
focused on reforming himself.

531
00:28:53,680 --> 00:28:54,960
He's also clever and diligent,

532
00:28:54,960 --> 00:28:55,400
so we let him

533
00:28:55,400 --> 00:28:56,830
deliver food to other prisoners.

534
00:28:56,830 --> 00:28:57,760
Half a month ago,

535
00:28:58,000 --> 00:28:59,860
Liu XVIII suddenly reported to me

536
00:29:00,000 --> 00:29:00,960
that this Liu XIX

537
00:29:01,680 --> 00:29:03,210
had gone on a hunger strike.

538
00:29:08,510 --> 00:29:09,240
Liu XVIII.

539
00:29:10,590 --> 00:29:12,110
He's become like this.

540
00:29:12,790 --> 00:29:14,790
Don't you bear any responsibility?

541
00:29:15,000 --> 00:29:16,110
He wants to die.

542
00:29:17,200 --> 00:29:18,620
What can I do?

543
00:29:19,310 --> 00:29:20,070
My life

544
00:29:20,070 --> 00:29:21,730
is already miserable enough.

545
00:29:22,270 --> 00:29:24,510
I don't have the energy to care about him.

546
00:29:24,510 --> 00:29:26,830
You think everything now

547
00:29:27,880 --> 00:29:28,790
is his fault?

548
00:29:30,590 --> 00:29:32,950
My future is ruined. I'm better off dead.

549
00:29:33,310 --> 00:29:34,500
Isn't it his fault?

550
00:29:36,750 --> 00:29:37,640
He went mad

551
00:29:38,070 --> 00:29:38,830
and wild

552
00:29:38,920 --> 00:29:40,240
because he lost

553
00:29:40,240 --> 00:29:42,340
his twin brother.

554
00:29:43,030 --> 00:29:44,200
This is the most basic emotion

555
00:29:44,200 --> 00:29:45,860
as a human being.

556
00:29:46,030 --> 00:29:46,830
And you

557
00:29:47,160 --> 00:29:49,140
are his last remaining relative

558
00:29:49,200 --> 00:29:50,440
in this world.

559
00:29:50,830 --> 00:29:52,200
Living in the same cell,

560
00:29:52,640 --> 00:29:54,310
have you ever cared about him?

561
00:29:58,790 --> 00:30:00,110
Your indifference

562
00:30:01,400 --> 00:30:03,950
is like a cold knife.

563
00:30:04,830 --> 00:30:06,550
You are killing your own brother,

564
00:30:06,550 --> 00:30:08,200
cut by cut.

565
00:30:11,030 --> 00:30:12,140
You feel wronged,

566
00:30:12,640 --> 00:30:14,570
and that I'm falsely accusing you?

567
00:30:17,720 --> 00:30:19,270
I didn't mean to do it.

568
00:30:19,640 --> 00:30:22,310
Despair has taken control of you.

569
00:30:23,790 --> 00:30:26,150
And you dare to call yourself a scholar.

570
00:30:26,510 --> 00:30:29,360
When Master Di was wrongfully imprisoned,

571
00:30:29,550 --> 00:30:31,000
his life was hanging by a thread

572
00:30:31,000 --> 00:30:32,430
but he never gave up.

573
00:30:32,590 --> 00:30:34,110
With his intelligence

574
00:30:34,200 --> 00:30:35,480
and his desire to live,

575
00:30:35,510 --> 00:30:37,310
he finally walked out of prison

576
00:30:37,480 --> 00:30:38,740
