678
00:37:48,820 --> 00:37:50,840
Recently in the capital, there's a saying

679
00:37:50,840 --> 00:37:51,640
going around,

680
00:37:51,800 --> 00:37:53,070
saying that the current Emperor

681
00:37:53,070 --> 00:37:55,320
is not the Retired Emperor's
legitimate eldest son.

682
00:37:55,320 --> 00:37:57,510
He cannot sustain the Tang Empire.

683
00:37:59,070 --> 00:38:01,110
Did you spread these rumours?

684
00:38:01,550 --> 00:38:03,550
This time, it truly wasn't me.

685
00:38:04,190 --> 00:38:05,190
It's because the news of him

686
00:38:05,190 --> 00:38:06,450
not being able to enjoy

687
00:38:06,510 --> 00:38:08,150
